  "description": "Rich, velvety and spiked with saffron, this Sardinian-inspired ragù will have you dining delizioso in minutes. Cook sausage meat in a fragrant tomato sauce, enrich it with butter and serve over indulgent spinach and ricotta ravioli. ",
